content: ActionOutline is designed to help you organize your ideas in a tree outline form. You can cut and paste branches, arrange items, place checks or tags next to listed items, print data, link to local or web files, and search information.

description: Outline created and used by ActionOutline, an application used to organize a user's thoughts and ideas; stores an outline layout, which includes information about text, styles, images and other items.
